Question: Is the speaker to the left of the device that is above the keyboard?

Reference Answer: No, the speaker is to the right of the monitor.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n315887.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='keyboard')
IMAGE0=CROP_ABOVE(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='device')
IMAGE1=CROP_LEFTOF(image=IMAGE0,box=BOX1)
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE1,object='speaker')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX2)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
